# Site Configuration
# ===================

# For custom domain deployment (root level)
SITE=https://your-domain.com
PUBLIC_BASE_PATH=/

# For GitHub Pages subpath deployment, use:
# SITE=https://username.github.io/
# PUBLIC_BASE_PATH=/repository-name

# GitHub API Token (Optional)
# ============================
# Enables live repository data fetching with higher rate limits
# Create a token at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Required scopes: read-only public repository access
GITHUB_TOKEN=
